{"tid":2197980,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普：不會延長 TikTok 交易期限　不賣掉就關門","createTime":"2020-09-11T04:34:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-11T05:09:15.000Z","uid":79562,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b9996b1e84fc71fdc3cfcbc7bba4c0b47b8a4f86","tid":2197980,"uid":79562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T04:34:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://external-hkt1-1.xx.fbcdn.net/safe_image.php?d=AQA7IwAVJm5WOsYz&amp;w=500&amp;h=261&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F20200801-15_KXIcQ_1200x630cropcenter.png&amp;cfs=1&amp;ext=jpg&amp;_nc_cb=1&amp;_nc_hash=AQCGUpi4cZFx78UK\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fexternal-hkt1-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fsafe_image.php%3Fd%3DAQA7IwAVJm5WOsYz%26w%3D500%26h%3D261%26url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fcdn.thestandnews.com%252Fmedia%252Fphotos%252Fcache%252F20200801-15_KXIcQ_1200x630cropcenter.png%26cfs%3D1%26ext%3Djpg%26_nc_cb%3D1%26_nc_hash%3DAQCGUpi4cZFx78UK&h=87d90163&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國總統特朗普表示，字節跳動於今個月 15 號最後限期前一定要完成出售 TikTok 在美國業務，否則 TikTok 必須終止營運。<br />\n<br />\n中國於上月 28 日發布「中國禁止出口限制出口技術目錄」，市場普遍認為，TikTok 的推薦頁面（ For You page）將被限制出售。字節跳動其後亦發聲明，表示交易可能要延至 11 月大選之後。後來再傳出 TikTok 的潛在買家同字節跳動研究不同交易結構，包括不收購關鏈軟件，以避免觸碰中國的新規定。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普於美國時間周四啟程去密歇根出席競選活動時向記者表示，出售 TikTok 的限期不會延長：「要麼關門，要麼賣掉。」<br />\n<br />\nTikTok 方面暫時未有回應。<br />\n<br />\n路透社"},{"pid":"ffb95488ef4c0d3760e09f3a39e64d8c9eb5d59c","tid":2197980,"uid":54303,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T04:43:09.000Z","msg":"執左佢最好，一蚊都唔好益支那豬"},{"pid":"71b65d44709ae580e06ae7bf45ceb0c8d50ddeaf","tid":2197980,"uid":1781,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T05:09:15.000Z","msg":"好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}